[[File:Point_Nadir.jpg|thumb|The Mines on the Point Nadir's map.]]
The '''Mines''' were located in the [[Point Nadir]], on the [[Comet/Legends|comet]] [[Resh 9376/Legends|Resh 9376]]. The sprawling caverns began at the [[Fissure District]] and were rumored to contain [[Salovan Fische]]' Legacy - a treasure trove full of goods and riches hidden in a remote cave. Though the majority of tunnels were unmapped, they attracted a large number of visitor and residents. [[Anjiliac]] clan occasionally send groups of [[Houk/Legends|Houk]] thugs to clear the mines, with little effect. In addition to common [[Mynock/Legends|mynocks]], the mines housed an undocumented spider-like predator, responsible for dozens of deaths.

